               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gadla Takla Hāymānot “Vita of Takla Haymanot” (fols. 4ra-7ra)
 II)
                     Maṣḥafa lǝdatu la-ʾabuna Takla Hāymānot “Book of the Genealogy of ʾabuna Takla
                     Haymanot” (fols. 7ra-8va)
 - Genealogy of Takla Hāymānot (fols.
                     7ra-8va)
 III) Gadla Takla Hāymānot “Vita of Takla Haymanot” (fols.
                     8va-110ra)
 - Introduction (fols. 8va-13rb)
 - Gadla Takla Hāymānot
                     “Vita of Takla Haymanot” (fols. 13rb-110ra)
 IV) Maṣḥafa fǝlsätu la-ʾabuna
                     Takla Hāymānot “Book of the Translation of ʾabuna Takla Haymanot” (fols.
                     110ra-120ra)
 V) Taʾammǝra Takla Hāymānot “Miracles of Takla Haymanot”: 19
                     miracles (fols. 120rb-131rb)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
