                  <provenance>The owner ʾato Bāyru Walda Lǝʿul  is mentioned in Additio 1; s.
                     supplication formulas <locus target="#108ra">108ra</locus>, 110ra, 123rb,
                     126ra). Besides, other individuals are mentioned in the supplication formulas:
                     Gabra Śǝllāse most frequently (<locus target="#10ra">10ra</locus>, 13ra, 52va,
                     58rb, 60rb, 69vb, 79ra, 89rb, 99ra, 105va, 108ra, 110ra, 110vb, 120ra, 120rb,
                     121ra), his mother Ḫiruta Śǝllāse (<locus target="#110ra">110ra</locus>, 123rb,
                     126va); others, possibly members of his family: Walatta Ṣādǝqān (<locus target="#10ra">10ra</locus>, 52va, 79ra, 89rb, 130va), Gabra ʾAragāwi
                     (<locus target="#10ra">10ra</locus>, 52va, 79ra, 99ra, 120ra), Walatta
                     Krǝstos (<locus target="#10ra">10ra</locus>, 60rb, 89rb, 110vb, 120ra), Gabra
                     Tǝnśʾe (<locus target="#10ra">10ra</locus>, 120ra, 121vb, 124ra, 125ra),
                     Walatta Kidān (<locus target="#10ra">10ra</locus>, 52va, 99ra, 110vb, 120ra),
                     Gabra Ṣādǝqān (<locus target="#58rb">58rb</locus>, 122ra, 124va, 125ra),
                     Walatta Yoḥannǝs (<locus target="#108ra">108ra</locus>, 120ra), Gabra Māryām
                     (<locus target="#108ra">108ra</locus>, 126va, 130ra), Gabra Krǝstos (<locus target="#124ra">124ra</locus>, 124va, 126ra, 127rb, 128rb), Walatta Wahǝd
                     (<locus target="#124vb">124vb</locus>, 129rb, 130ra, 130va).</provenance>
